title: VA Indie Rock September 2013 - Your Wish (Dutch Treat I4 HQ)
description:
The seventh Indie playlist from September 2013 is a bit different than intended. I had to mix several Rock genres a bit. So here and there the list may sound a bit jumpy (keeps you awake). HQ wherever possible with Rock and MP3. I'm quite happy with it..... Enjoy,

PS Sorry no cover because the software does not work again.
